# 🏥 Medical Appointment System — FastAPI

A production-style REST API built with FastAPI and Python.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Python
- FastAPI
- Pydantic
- Swagger UI

## ✅ Features
- Doctor & Appointment CRUD
- JWT-ready Auth structure
- Search, Filter, Sort, Pagination
- Business rule validations (duplicate check, delete guard)
- 3-step workflow: Book → Confirm → Complete
- Auto Swagger UI docs

## 🚀 Run Locally
pip install fastapi uvicorn
uvicorn main:app --reload

## 📖 API Docs
Visit: http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs
```

